## Troubleshooting

| Problem | Check |
|---------|-------|
| Site down | `docker compose ps`, `ufw status` |
| API 502 | `curl http://10.99.0.3:8000/api/health` from VPS, `wg show` |
| SSL error | `openssl x509 -in /opt/flowmanner/certs/fullchain.pem -noout -dates` |
| Frontend not updating | `docker compose build frontend && docker compose up -d --no-deps frontend` |
